
Not yet implemented but planned features:

    * Drop privileges
    * Check if the config file has actually changed before writing to it
    * Restart nagios (if config has changed)
    * Execute nagios config check to make sure the config files are correct befor restarting nagios
    * Logfiles

Features under consideration:
    * Some way for nagios to check if this tool has been run in the last x hours
    * Some way for nagios to check if there where errors in the last run

